msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#, no-wrap
msgid "Storing Sensitive Documents\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**The persistent storage is not hidden.** An attacker in possession of the USB\n"
"stick can know that there is a persistent storage on it. Take into consideration\n"
"that you can be forced or tricked to give out its passphrase.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Remember also that **secure deletion do not work as expected on USB sticks.**<br/>\n"
"[[See the corresponding documentation.|encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion#index2h1]]\n"
msgstr ""

